"Ohhh...shiny ship."  Waspinator admired as he saw the shuttle in 
the shy.

"Wha-" Quickstrike started seeing it in the sky, upon noting that it 
was not predacon he continued "Slag it!"  he shouted and opened fire 
on the spacecraft with energy blasts from his snake arm.

Inferno positioned himself behind a rock croutching down and leveled 
his gun at the shuttle awaiting any occupents that may leave it.
